 "remarks": "Welcome to effortless living in the heart of Mid City! This spacious 2-bedroom, 2-bath ranch-style condo blends modern updates with unbeatable convenience. The showpiece kitchen offers sleek finishes and contemporary style, creating the perfect space for cooking, entertaining, or simply enjoying your morning coffee. The open-concept layout provides an airy flow between the living and dining spaces, making everyday living both comfortable and inviting. Oversized primary bedroom boasts spa-like full bath with double vanity and oversized shower. Need extra space? The finished lower level offers endless flexibility-ideal for a playroom, home gym, office, media room, or cozy family room. Carport and storage room add to the perfection. Nothing to do but move right in and start enjoying all this home has to offer. Perfectly situated for commuters with quick access to both the Merritt Parkway and I-95, while also being walking distance to shopping, restaurants, and conveniences. Just minutes from downtown Stamford&apos;s vibrant nightlife, featuring first-class dining, theaters, movies, entertainment, and more. This is modern condo living at its best!",
